Package model

Class AnalysisSubject

java.lang.Object
model.ViewerSubject
model.AnalysisSubject
public class AnalysisSubject
extends ViewerSubject
This class is an concrete subject which contains the results of an analysis for its Viewers to observe.

AnalysisSubject inherits from ViewerSubject. It holds an Analysis type object which can perform an analysis and store the results within the AnalysisSubject for reference by the attached observers.

Author:
Matthew Da Silva
